data.description: *NEW PRICE* Live, Work, Study & Play in the crossroads between Manoa & Kaimuki; Nestled along the Palolo Stream lies a rarely available Condominium: Waialae Place, which is a short distance from Manoa UH & University of Honolulu, 1 Min access to H1, King St & Kapiolani Blvd giving you access to everything the Hawaiian Metropolis has to offer. Perched atop the second floor, this Professionally designed 445 Sq Ft, 1 Bedroom 1 Bath Condo is ideally placed for tranquil water views & smart interior spaces for maximum enjoyment. The unit features matching Kitchen & Bath Cabinetry & Countertops, Bar area, Designer Ledger Stone & Accent Walls & an indoor-outdoor feeling Entertainment space that connects to the open air access from the sliding glass door. 2 Wall A/C units keep the different spaces cool day or night. Outside you'll enjoy a community Pool & BBQ area, along with an on-site manager & your dedicated covered parking space and personal storage locker.
